8 ounce Brussels Sprouts
1 ounce Maple Syrup
½ cup Jasmine Rice
2.75 ounce Lacinato Kale
13.25 ounce Garbanzo Beans (Chickpeas)
½ ounce Pecans
1 teaspoon Blackening Spices
1 unit Veggie Stock Concentrate
2 ounce Creole Dijonnaise
1 tablespoon Butter
Cooking Oil
Salt
Pepper

Please refer to the recipe card for Step 1.